mcp_prompt:
Select the single best skill-oriented agent for the following task.

Selection rules:
1. Match the task against `when_to_use` first.
2. Reject skills whose `when_not_to_use` conflicts with the request.
3. Prefer stronger non-legacy skills.
4. Use `allowed_tools`, `memory`, and `output_contract` as tie-breakers.
5. If no skill is appropriate, return an empty agent name so the runtime can answer directly.

Available Work Agents:
{{range $i, $tool := .assign_param}}- Agent Name: {{$tool.tool_name}}
  Agent Description: {{$tool.tool_desc}}
  Memory: {{$tool.tool_memory}}
  When To Use: {{$tool.tool_when_to_use}}
  When Not To Use: {{$tool.tool_when_not_to_use}}
  Instructions: {{$tool.tool_instructions}}
  Output Contract: {{$tool.tool_output_contract}}
  Allowed Tools: {{$tool.tool_allowed_tools}}
  Triggers: {{$tool.tool_triggers}}
  Legacy: {{$tool.tool_legacy}}
{{end}}

